  "prompt": "What countries participate in The Commonwealth Games?",
  "response": "The Commonwealth Games is a multi-sport event in which athletes from the Commonwealth of Nations participate. The Commonwealth of Nations comprises 56 member countries, most of which are former territories of the British Empire. Below is a list of the countries that typically participate in the Commonwealth Games:\n\n### Africa\n1. Botswana\n2. Cameroon\n3. Eswatini\n4. The Gambia\n5. Ghana\n6. Kenya\n7. Lesotho\n8. Malawi\n9. Mauritius\n10. Mozambique\n11. Namibia\n12. Nigeria\n13. Rwanda\n14. Seychelles\n15. Sierra Leone\n16. South Africa\n17. Tanzania\n18. Uganda\n19. Zambia\n\n### Americas\n20. Bahamas\n21. Belize\n22. Bermuda\n23. Canada\n24. Falkland Islands\n25. Guyana\n26. Saint Lucia\n27. Saint Vincent and the Grenadines\n\n### Asia\n28. Bangladesh\n29. Brunei\n30. India\n31. Malaysia\n32. Maldives\n33. Pakistan\n34. Singapore\n35. Sri Lanka\n\n### Europe\n36. Cyprus\n37. England\n38. Gibraltar\n39. Guernsey\n40. Isle of Man\n41. Jersey\n42. Malta\n43. Northern Ireland\n44. Scotland\n45. Wales\n\n### Oceania\n46. Australia\n47. Cook Islands\n48. Fiji\n49. Kiribati\n50. Nauru\n51. New Zealand\n52. Niue\n53. Norfolk Island\n54. Papua New Guinea\n55. Samoa\n56. Solomon Islands\n57. Tonga\n58. Tuvalu\n59. Vanuatu\n\n### Caribbean\n60. Anguilla\n61. Antigua and Barbuda\n62. Barbados\n63. British Virgin Islands\n64. Cayman Islands\n65. Dominica\n66. Grenada\n67. Montserrat\n68. Saint Kitts and Nevis\n69. Trinidad and Tobago\n70. Turks and Caicos Islands\n\nThese countries and territories are eligible to participate in the Commonwealth Games, although participation may vary depending on the specific edition of the event. Some territories, like the Falkland Islands, Gibraltar, and the British Virgin Islands, are not independent nations but are still part of the Commonwealth and participate in the Games.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
